Sampo Kellomäki (MSc. CS, Helsinki University of Technology) was the
lead architect of the TAS3 project and is currently CTO of Synergetics
NV, specializing in personal data stores and commercializing TAS3
research results. Prior to Synergetics, he participated in Liberty
Alliance and OASIS standardization. He is also the founder of the
zxid.org open source project, implementing TAS3 technologies. His
background is in virtual directories and identity management.

